Package: kiwix
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends},
 ${misc:Depends}
Description: offline Wikipedia reader
 Kiwix allows you to read and search through offline content
 as they were online. Similar to a browser, Kiwix works with
 the highly compressed ZIM file format.
 .
 Features:
   * Pure ZIM file reader
   * Case and diacritics insensitive full text search engine
   * Bookmarks & Notes
   * ZIM base HTTP server
   * PDF/HTML export
   * Localized
   * Search suggestions
   * ZIM file Index capacity
   * Tabs navigation
